Subject: [PATCH] Add AI Governance offering; SEO + AI answer-engine
 optimization

- New AI Governance section ($4,500 engagement + $6,500 bundle), nav/footer links
- FAQ section with matching FAQPage schema
- JSON-LD: ProfessionalService entity + full service/offer catalog
- Canonical URL, og:image + logo assets, updated titles/descriptions
- robots.txt (AI crawlers allowed), sitemap.xml, llms.txt
- Switch all contact email to info@watusoft.com
- Fix checklist download path (/files/) and footer mailto
